Title: AutoNav.NET
Description: AutoNav.NET is an ASP.NET control that is designed to easily generate navigation elements (main navigation, breadcrumbs, sub-navigation) programmatically with minimal setup.  It is designed to work with Sitefinity CMS or as a standalone .NET control.

Project Description
AutoNav.NET is an ASP.NET control that is designed to easily generate navigation elements (main navigation, breadcrumbs, sub-navigation) programmatically with minimal setup. It is designed to work with Sitefinity CMS or as a standalone .NET control.

Designed by the team at Graphically Speaking.
